"{\n    \"explanation\": \"The paper focuses on the use of digital health systems for self-care training in type 2 diabetes patients, specifically examining interventions like blood glucose monitoring, physical activity, and medication adherence, which aligns with continuous glucose monitoring (CGM) data and the broader concept of electronic health records. The review also incorporates elements of clinical notes due to the analysis of patient data and interventions.\",\n    \"class_labels\": [\"continuous_glucose_monitoring_(cgm)_data\", \"electronic_health_records\", \"clinical_notes_(natural_language_processing)\"]\n}"